      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOTION ACTIVATED (2) copped a check in the run and boxed on to place when a 3 length third (20.48) in a Maiden at this track. Well worth another try. MOCKERY MIRAGE (1) scored his first victory last start at this track over 366m (20.20). Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Sure to measure up. CYCLONE LEO (6) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind MOCKERY MIRAGE (20.28) in a Maiden. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Hard to beat again. MIDGET EMERALD (7) is an improver who can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track when making debut.",
